WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.840
Conflict is inevitable. You rarely prevent it. In many ways, it drives progress. What matters is

00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:11.420
how you handle it. You've learned how to navigate it with clarity and turn it into something

00:00:11.420 --> 00:00:18.500
constructive. I'll see you later, Alex. Until then, handle conflict with intent and make it work for you.
